1 node storage TACC 
10GB TPC-H and TPC-DS stored on separate drive mounted onto /mnt

first tpch data loaded, then
all tpch queries run one after another 
repeat that 9 times ( so same query isn't run 9 straight times, but rather whole workload run 9 times)
then exit and repeat with tpcds

repeated this with each listener implementation and a vanilla implementation on
modified spark and TODO vanilla spark 

"spark_mod_internal_listener" directory is all listeners run on modified spark.
"spark_vanilla_internal_listener" will be all listeners except for row-group (as
that can only run with modified spark) run with out of the box spark.
